# Endless Academy - Project Guidelines

## Font System

- **Primary Font**: Poppins (modern, geometric sans-serif)
- **Display Font**: Poppins (same for consistency)
- Use `font-display` class for all major headings and titles
- Use `font-sans` (default) for body text
- Poppins weights available: 300 (Light), 400 (Regular), 500 (Medium), 600 (Semibold), 700 (Bold), 800 (Extrabold), 900 (Black)

## Design Principles

- Modern, animated, and vibrant design
- Gradient backgrounds (primary-600 to pink-600)
- Smooth transitions and hover effects
- Glassmorphism effects where appropriate
- Responsive design (mobile-first)

## Card Layout

- All cards must use `flex flex-col h-full` for consistent height
- Content sections should use `flex-grow` to fill space
- Use `mt-auto` for bottom-aligned content
- Grid containers should use `items-stretch` class

## Color Scheme

- Primary: Red gradient (#dc2626 to #b91c1c)
- Accent: Pink (#ec4899)
- Use gradient text for important headings
- Shadows: Multiple levels (shadow-lg, shadow-xl, shadow-2xl)

## Animation Classes

- animate-fade-in
- animate-slide-in-left / animate-slide-in-right
- animate-scale-in
- animate-float
- animate-gradient

## Component Guidelines

- Buttons: Use btn-primary or btn-secondary classes
- Cards: Use card or card-gradient classes
- Titles: Use section-title and section-subtitle classes
